  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
          <h1>AirBike</h1>
          <p>You have no idea what is AirBike, how it works, so I'm here to help you. We are a kool oganization run by kool team. We would like to do something to improve environment in Saigon, to bring back fresh air to this lovely city. We encourage you use environment friendly mean like bicycle to help reduce air pollution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
          <h1>3 Easy Steps</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 num-style">
          <h2><span>1: Grab a Bicycle</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 num-style">
          <h2><span>2: Earn AirCredit</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 num-stlye">
          <h2><span>3: Reward Yourself</span></h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Instructions -->
    <section id="instructions" class="instructions-section">
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-lg-8 offset-lg-2'>
          <h1>Grab a Bicycle</h1>
          <p>With or without a registered account, you are able to rent a bicyle.</p>
          <p>However, I would like to suggest you to regester an account, in order to earn your AirCredit.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-default page-scroll" href="#services">Earn AirCredit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section id="services" class="services-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h1>Earn AirCredit</h1>
            <p>For each mile riding on our bicycle, you earn 1 AirCredit point.</p>
            <p>The more you riding the more AirCredit you earning.</p>
            <p>With our AirCredit, you can use them to buy food, clothes vouchers and much more.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-default page-scroll" href="#contact">Reward yourself</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h1>Reward yourself</h1>
            <p>Use your AirCredit to buy food, clothes vouchers and much more.</p>
            <p>You earn this, you deserve it, enjoy it.</p>
            <p>Are you ready to earn your reward by riding with us? What are you waiting for? Click below button</p>
            <a class="btn btn-default page-scroll" href="<%= new_user_path %>">Sign Up</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
